</style><h2 id="outline__5" class="wp-block-heading">一条里里香</h2><figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AIL4fc9WDTf2X56_h4xcerpPRN_u2uu2dGLBq1xhbY8Ztmu9RJAo1c7IH15Q6TRWyAj1GFtAmidKmRcVD9ELHKwWVKxBMWOjlz9JZhyZCoM2nIoqkrsCIs28MLy8_KZNd2wHiMrMXGtUkyzeHvGFH0V5djsW=w1097-h617-s-no" alt="" width="401" height="226"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © 2016 COVER Corp.</figcaption></figure><p></p><p>崭露头角的女总统。该公司是出于好奇而成立的，但到目前为止进展顺利。他善于与人沟通，也亲自处理与海外公司的谈判。成功的关键是睡好觉。另一方面，她的个人生活也有很多坎坷的地方，而且她总体上不太擅长做家务。</p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-table is-style-stripes"><table><tbody><tr><td>角色设计</td><td>中村</td></tr><tr><td>官方渠道</td><td><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@IchijouRirika" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="Ririka Ch. Ririka Ichijo - ReGLOSS">Ririka Ch. Ririka Ichijo - ReGLOSS</a></td></tr><tr><td> X（推特）公众号</td><td><a href="https://twitter.com/ichijouririka" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="一条梨香🌃ReGLOSS">一条里里香<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f303.png" alt="🌃" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />重新光泽度</a></td></tr><tr><td>预定首发交付日期</td><td>2023年（令和5年）<br> 9月9日（周六）21:00~ </td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="“一条梨香”首张预告#ReGLOSS" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/lDEdjNkPK-I?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"> <a href="https://twitter.com/ichijouririka/status/1698591778906292475" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AIL4fc_egYfJMVNBRSkC-7JExsNqXp06ERPI4VHHJVyN70UiaRuDmVHVs5QdRTseNApfeI388K-l4E6eeT7Gr71Q2RSkYFMGkLLAnrr5T4vD1PFLhvy1fSDehyvtXbEdt1QA2SMoC-c9Q0yLotQiCpWm-hqw=w1097-h1536-s-no" alt=""/></a></figure><p></p><h2 id="outline__6" class="wp-block-heading">聚风亭拉登</h2><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AIL4fc_JZ5D4XX5YuQiBrY-QSmw08BeaDEPDBvCdVvT5asmjbh9sUzhMUI2mFKFyOslTDleNArotdEc6Jww4g-nfo0AOxpSVYz6YA2SsNeGh7qUmnRioFOf38NTBPeZfhSCltkuRXRUEzNltBIek5J9gTKhC=w1097-h617-s-no" alt=""/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © 2016 COVER Corp.</figcaption></figure><p></p><p>一位祖母的孩子，既传统又创新，对单口相声表演者有着浪漫的兴趣。他热爱新旧、日本和西方的文化和表演艺术。这绝不是由过量饮酒引起的。遇到落语后，她更加喜欢说话，也开始挑战自己创作故事。</p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-table is-style-stripes"><table><tbody><tr><td>角色设计</td><td>超民</td></tr><tr><td>官方渠道</td><td><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@JuufuuteiRaden" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="Raden Ch. Juubutei Raden - ReGLOSS">Raden Ch. Juubutei Raden - ReGLOSS</a></td></tr><tr><td> X（推特）公众号</td><td><a href="https://twitter.com/juufuuteiraden" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="儒家乌夫泰·拉登🐚ReGLOSS">由布亭螺钿<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f41a.png" alt="🐚" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />重新光泽度</a></td></tr><tr><td>预定首发交付日期</td><td>2023年（令和5年）<br> 9月10日（周日）20:00~ </td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="“Jufuutei Laden”首张预告#ReGLOSS" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VLXGf3uE8Gc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"> <a href="https://twitter.com/juufuuteiraden/status/1698592037824840174" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopen